description: Publishes a listing (a record of an asset at a given time) or removes a listing from the catalog.

parameters.name: action
parameters.description: Specifies whether to publish or unpublish a listing.

parameters.name: clientToken
parameters.description: A unique, case-sensitive identifier that is provided to ensure the idempotency of the request. This field is autopopulated if not provided.

parameters.name: domainIdentifier
parameters.description: The ID of the Amazon DataZone domain.

nested_items.name: listingId
nested_items.description: The ID of the listing (a record of an asset at a given time).

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: Specifies the status of the listing.
